{"tid":1718282,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有手足俾人暗殺 黑衫青年荃灣離奇重傷胸口大量流血雙手骨折 不省人事送院搶救不治","createTime":"2019-11-13T21:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T03:34:44.000Z","uid":259010,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a68507f0452aacae8fbf1d30d2786e34c1ecdab3","tid":1718282,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T21:53:00.000Z","msg":"周三（13日）大約10時30分，有市民發現一名年約20多歲、穿黑色衫的年青男子，背部朝天倒臥在荃灣嘉里物流中心外的行人路地上，雙手懷疑骨折，胸口附近有大量血迹及失去知覺，臉部亦有流血，地上遺下大灘血迹。男子被送往仁濟醫院搶救，延至晚上約11時多證實不治。"},{"pid":"66d91670d9bca562a22fe9e261e08058a5d9d390","tid":1718282,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T22:06:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191113&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60264041\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191113%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60264041&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=c5f2c578\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191113%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60264041&h=38243f1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191113&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60264041</a>"},{"pid":"8798f72bc9208877d272d41236ea9a7b6cc26ea3","tid":1718282,"uid":263994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T22:19:07.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"fd4ad706257bbab7dffae7831fdc0ba5d664fdd4","tid":1718282,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:12:29.000Z","msg":"點解推唔上去"},{"pid":"a0f7039a82c1e0123ddf1cd97a537dd59a105e77","tid":1718282,"uid":1305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8ac5c92dbc46e53fd735c28407338380dd3742","tid":171